skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: i want tea
des:
Tea fun provides fun the whole family can enjoy and is guaranteed to make you smile. The skill will ask continous questions about how do you prefer your tea.

To start, just say "Alexa, I want tea", "Alexa Open I want tea" or "Alexa, launch I want tea" to get started.

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
